    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    Applicant
    Represents an applicant in the BTO system.
    ApplicantInterface
    User interface for applicants in the BTO system.
    ApplicationController
    The ApplicationController class manages BTO (Build-To-Order) housing project applications.
    ApplicationStatus
    Represents the possible statuses of an application in the system.
    AuthController
    The AuthController class manages user authentication and user account management for the BTO housing system.
    BookingController
    The BookingController class manages the flat booking process for BTO (Build-To-Order) housing projects.
    BTOManagementSystem
    Main entry point for the BTO (Build-To-Order) Management System.
    Enquiry
    The Enquiry class represents a question or request for information submitted by an applicant.
    EnquiryController
    The EnquiryController class manages enquiries in the BTO housing system.
    FileManager
    Manages file operations for the BTO system including loading and saving data.
    FilterCriteria
    The FilterCriteria class provides a flexible way to define and apply filtering criteria for BTO housing entities like projects, applications, and bookings.
    FlatBooking
    The FlatBooking class represents a booking made by an applicant for a specific flat in a BTO project.
    FlatType
    Represents the available types of flats in the system.
    HDBManager
    Represents an HDB manager in the BTO system.
    HDBOfficer
    Represents an HDB officer in the BTO system.
    ManagerInterface
    Provides the user interface and interaction logic for HDB Manager users in the BTO (Build-To-Order) Management System.
    MaritalStatus
    Represents the marital status of an individual in the system.
    OfficerInterface
    Provides the user interface and interaction logic for HDB Officer users in the BTO (Build-To-Order) Management System.
    OfficerRegistration
    The OfficerRegistration class represents a registration request from an HDB officer to work on a specific BTO project.
    Project
    The Project class represents a Build-To-Order (BTO) housing project.
    ProjectApplication
    The ProjectApplication class represents an application submitted by an applicant for a BTO housing project.
    ProjectController
    The ProjectController class manages BTO (Build-To-Order) housing projects in the system.
    ProjectFlats
     
    Receipt
    The Receipt class represents a booking receipt for a BTO flat.
    ReceiptGenerator
    The ReceiptGenerator class creates formatted receipts for BTO flat bookings.
    RegistrationController
    The RegistrationController class manages officer registrations for BTO housing projects.
    Report
    Represents a report for flat bookings with configurable filtering and tracking.
    ReportController
    The ReportController class manages the generation and formatting of reports for the BTO housing system.
    User
     
    UserInterface
    Main user interface for the BTO (Build-To-Order) Management System.
    Withdrawal
    Represents a withdrawal request for a project application.
    WithdrawalController
    Controller class responsible for managing withdrawal requests from applicants.
